reviewText: I bought this because I have really enjoyed John Feeley's Chaconne that I have seen on YouTube however this disc will not play on my Samsung Blue Ray Player because it says it is for the wrong region.  I will be returning this because of that fact.
I am a Classical Guitarist myself and a BIG fan od Bach have listen to many artists reditions of Bach 's music and have found no others who come close to the depth of Mr. Feeley's!
